org.zaproxy.zap.extension.websocket

Class WebSocketMessageDTO

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.zaproxy.zap.extension.websocket.WebSocketMessageDTO
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Message
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    WebSocketFuzzMessageDTO

    public class WebSocketMessageDTO
extends Object
implements Message
    Data Transfer Object used for displaying WebSockets communication. Intended to decouple user interface representation from version specific WebSocketMessage.
